name: Signed Range Nicaraguan Churchill
additionalNotes:
http://www.cigarking.com/CIGARS/CIGARS-BY-THE-BOX/DUNHILL-SIGNED-RANGE

There are two versions of the Dunhill Signed Range. This is the Nicaraguan version made since 2007.  The cigar band has the Dunhill name in cursive, surmounted with a crest and with "since 1907" below.  The older Dominican version has “DUNHILL” in block letters.
